# UI Primitives

Read `frontend/src/components/ui/AGENTS.md` before editing or adding primitives.

Required pattern: `import * as React`, `forwardRef`, `displayName`, exported `FooProps`, `cn()` for classes, CVA for variants.

Do not add API calls, hooks, or domain types to `ui/` files.
